{"tid":2111391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前男警涉向妻子胞姐騙財致婚姻破裂 疑拍下夫妻行房影片要求兒子觀看","createTime":"2020-07-16T13:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T14:03:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5bcf244175033899154de605a9158e8c4dfc29cb","tid":2111391,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/OEOQ654FQOH743BCUOPFC3XE5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FOEOQ654FQOH743BCUOPFC3XE5Y%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=6dd31a08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FOEOQ654FQOH743BCUOPFC3XE5Y%2F&h=2543c9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/OEOQ654FQOH743BCUOPFC3XE5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n45歲前男警涉向妻子的胞姐訛稱兒子患病，成功騙取近20萬元，其後真相曝光，導致前男警與妻子分居。其後社署介入個案，兒子疑向社工透露，父親曾拍下與妻子行房的過程，並要求兒子觀看片段，又帶同兒子往公廁自慰。前男警被控欺詐及向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為等罪，今於粉嶺裁判法院再訊。裁判官將案件押後至8月14日。前男警須還柙候訊，但將於下周四進行保釋覆核申請。"},{"pid":"b2a779bcd5d3073a21ab0070ed81cc719bf1e07d","tid":2111391,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e486d5eefe248348c88c4e3c84f7648bc76c997f","tid":2111391,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a779bcd5d3073a21ab0070ed81cc719bf1e07d","tid":2111391,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\